<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>This is the adorable moment a baby enjoys her first ice cream cone - by diving into it face first! </p>

<p>The nine-month-old baby, called Emma, seemed to be enjoying the sweet treat as she tries to get as much of the ice cream into her mouth as possible.  </p>

<p>She grabs at the cone with both hands at a Dairy Queen restaurant in the US while being held by her great-grandmother.</p>

<p>Nine-month-old baby Emma enjoys the sweet treat as she tries to get as much of the ice cream into her mouth as possible</p>

<p>Her great-grandmother barely gets a chance to lick the cone before Emma opens her mouth wide and tries to eat some more.   </p>

<p>The baby loves the ice cream so much she plunges into it and ends up with both hands covered in it as she grabs it. </p>

<p>Emma seems very happy with herself, and waves her arms around in excitement, covering her great-grandmother with the frozen dessert in the process. </p>

<p>She grabs at the ice cream with both hands at a Dairy Queen restaurant in the US while her great-grandmother tries to lick the cone</p>

<p>The person taking the video is in hysterics at the baby reaching for the cone and trying to bite into it. </p>

<p>Hungry Emma ends up with ice cream all over her face and drops some on her pink top as she enjoys it.  </p>

<p>The video was taken on June 13, 2017, but has recently resurfaced.  </p>

<p> Hungry Emma ends up with ice cream all over her face and drops some on her pink top as she shoves it in her face </p>
